*圣菲利普 （St. Philip, 1412-14），Nanni di Banco<ref>{{cite web | last = Sullivan | first = Mary Ann | date = 2005年7月10日 | url = http://www.bluffton.edu/~sullivanm/orsanmichele/nanniphilip.html | title = ''St. Philip'', Orsanmichele | work = Orsanmichele | publisher = Digital Imaging Project: Art historical images of European and North American architecture and sculpture from classical Greek to Post-modern | accessdate = 2006年7月14日 | archive-date = 2015年4月19日 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150419125217/http://www.bluffton.edu/~sullivanm/orsanmichele/nanniphilip.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://employees.oneonta.edu/farberas/arth/Images/ARTH213images/Orsanmichele/NannidiBanco_Quattro.jpg | title = ''St. Philip'' | format = JPG | accessdate = 2006年7月14日 | archive-date = 2016年3月4日 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304022839/http://employees.oneonta.edu/farberas/arth/Images/ARTH213images/Orsanmichele/NannidiBanco_Quattro.jpg | dead-url = yes }}</ref> - 鞋匠捐建
